      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/583290655_18174144982370414_118817368069654967_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc2OTY2MDg2NDA3NzYxNTE4Mg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0MzZ4MTkwOC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=_r6lg840hisQ7kNvwFEvyUz&amp;_nc_oc=AdqO4l-9fGiMP8YOONAjuwvWqwxWU7XJ6ZVSOASmBlZwjc3Dn3ib0bZ7EQtVT8xaHdo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=W4Yr8bne5dKVRCRqbAu9cg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfycpkLQO9BK0icHAY1g3qSIcwZ9BJei1Q8t0Bi5YtQHMA&amp;oe=69CA2D21" alt="Instagram billede fra @poolsuite" /></p><p><strong>@poolsuite</strong></p><p>IMPORTANT COMPANY ANNOUNCEMENT: As the fiscal year comes to a close, it is our great pleasure to cordially invite all Vacation® employees, friends, and family to the 2025 Vacation® &amp; Poolsuite Office Holiday Party at @grampswynwood. <br/>
<br/>
Join Vacation® employees and enthusiasts alike for a corporate festivity featuring @malibudrinksus , Poolsuite DJs, and cross-departmental banter at the iconic Gramps in Wynwood. This remarkable venue has served Miami for over a decade, and with it closing in January, we’re honored to have them host our annual end-of-year celebration.<br/>
<br/>
Now, this wouldn’t be a Vacation® holiday party without an exceptional headliner to elevate the event. As such, we are proud to announce that French musician, producer, and DJ sensation @Mydsound will be joining us onstage to headline the evening’s festivities. <br/>
<br/>
Please find additional event details below and if you’re interested in attending, please RSVP at the link in our biography or visit rsvp.vacation.inc — and as always, leisure awaits.<br/>
<br/>
🌴 EVENT DETAILS 🌴 <br/>
<br/>
🍹 WHAT: Malibu Presents: The 2025 Vacation® &amp; Poolsuite Office Holiday Party<br/>
📅 WHEN: Friday, Dec 5, 2025 — 8 PM<br/>
📍 WHERE: Gramps in Wynwood (176 NW 24th St, Miami, FL 33127)<br/>
👔WEAR: “Corporate Chic” Attire<br/>
📝 RSVP: This party is free to attend - simply RSVP at rsvp.vacation.inc<br/>
<br/>
ENJOY:<br/>
<br/>
✓ Headlining musical talent @Mydsound<br/>
✓ Complimentary Malibu Beverages*<br/>
✓ Free Vacation® Brand Products*<br/>
✓ @poolsuite DJs<br/>
✓ Corporate Headshot Photo Booth<br/>
✓ Malibu Ice Luge<br/>
✓ Cross-Departmental Banter<br/>
<br/>
*Available While Supplies Last. Ages 21+</p>]]></description>
